snippet.title: Super Cream 64: The Grand Finale - Release Trailer (links in desc)
snippet.description:
After the lackluster "final" update, I wanted to go back and actually give this hack a proper farewell. And after over a year of on and off working, it's finally here! We have:

- Proper Flying
- New Alternative Outfits (only half of them in N64 build due to limited memory)
- New levels
- More Music
- and much more!

Logo for those who want it: https://i.imgur.com/WLoY5bI.png

A big thank you to everyone whose supported this whole endeavor and stuck around to the very end. Seriously, thank you. 

Links:
N64: https://romhacking.com/hack/super-cream-64
PC: https://github.com/Gamebunn/sm64ex-alo
